程序包 model.mapping

类 ClientMapping

java.lang.Object
model.mapping.ClientMapping
public class ClientMapping
extends java.lang.Object
Map Client data to JSON database. This "JSON database" is a self-defined database and it should only be used in this software.
Offering add, delete, modify and find methods for client data, which include (User, Coach and Administrator). In this class, we use JSON to manage our Client POJO.
从以下版本开始:
8 May 2021
版本:
1.4
作者:
Yubo Wu
另请参阅:
JSON, Client, User, Coach, Administrator

  • 方法详细资料

    • add

      public static <T extends Client> int add​(T type) throws java.io.IOException
      Add client(User, Coach, Administrator) to JSON database.
      类型参数:
      T - extends Client class
      参数:
      type - instance of class extended Client class
      返回:
      status code: DUPLICATE_ID, DUPLICATE_NICKNAME or SUCCESS
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur

    • delete

      public static int delete​(int id) throws java.io.IOException
      Delete Client(User, Coach, Administrator) from JSON database.
      参数:
      id - ID of the Client instance which you want to delete
      返回:
      Status code: CLIENT_NOT_FOUND or SUCCESS
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur

    • cancel

      public static int cancel​(int id) throws java.io.IOException
      Cancel Client(User, Coach, Administrator) account. Lazy deletion. That is, to set "cancel" to true.
      参数:
      id - ID of the Client instance which you want to delete
      返回:
      Status code: CLIENT_NOT_FOUND or SUCCESS
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur

    • modify

      public static <T extends Client> int modify​(T type) throws java.io.IOException
      Update Client(User, Coach, Administrator) data in JSON database. The method need ID to locate where the data is so do not set a new value to the ID.
      NOTE: You can not use this method to modify avatarSrc or recordHistory in Client. If you want to modify them, you need to use modifyAvatar(int, String).
      类型参数:
      T - extends Client class
      参数:
      type - updated instance of client class extended Client
      返回:
      status code: DUPLICATE_NICKNAME, CLIENT_NOT_FOUND or SUCCESS
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur
      另请参阅:
      modifyAvatar(int, String)

    • modifyRecordHistory

      public static int modifyRecordHistory​(int id, Client.RecordHistory history) throws java.io.IOException
      Update Client(User, Coach and Administrator} recordHistory data.
      If the history you want to modified not exist, then add it to database automatically. If exist, then modify it.
      NOTE: If you want to modify recordHistory and the data itself simultaneously, you need to call this method first.
      参数:
      id - Client id you want to modified
      history - history record you want to modified
      返回:
      status code: CLIENT_NOT_FOUND or SUCCESS
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur

    • modifyAvatar

      public static int modifyAvatar​(int id, java.lang.String originalPath) throws java.io.IOException
      Update Client(User, Coach and Administrator} avatar data. It will first copy the image to AVATAR_PATH, then update the srcPath of image to JSON database.
      参数:
      id - Client id you want to modify
      originalPath - the original path of the profile photo. Must be absolute path
      返回:
      NOT_IMAGE or SUCCESS
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur

    • find

      public static java.util.ArrayList<Client> find​(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String> map) throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
      Find client(User, Coach, Administrator) from JSON database, and return the results to a ArrayList. The parameter are HashMap, you need to put all AND conditions in hashmap. This find method can't handle other conditions except AND, like OR or BETWEEN or others.
      参数:
      map - the WHERE conditions are represented by K-V pairs using HashMap
      返回:
      ArrayList contained results.
      抛出:
      java.io.FileNotFoundException - when DATA_PATH not found

    • find

      public static java.util.ArrayList<Client> find​(java.lang.String key, java.lang.String value) throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
      Find client(User, Coach, Administrator) from JSON database, and return the results to a ArrayList. This method supports fuzzy search. This method require a key-value pair. It a simple version of find(HashMap). If you have only one condition to search, you can use this method.
      参数:
      key - the key of the value you want to search
      value - the value you want to search
      返回:
      ArrayList contained results.
      抛出:
      java.io.FileNotFoundException - when DATA_PATH not found

    • findUser

      public static java.util.ArrayList<User> findUser​(java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,​java.lang.String> map) throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
      Find User from JSON database, return the result to an ArrayList. The difference between the method and find(HashMap) is that the return value of this method will contains the instances of User, not Client.
      参数:
      map - the WHERE conditions are represented by K-V pairs using HashMap
      返回:
      ArrayList contained results.
      抛出:
      java.io.FileNotFoundException - when DATA_PATH not found
      另请参阅:
      find(HashMap)

      Find Coach from JSON database, return the result to an ArrayList. The difference between the method and find(HashMap) is that the return value of this method will contains the instances of Coach, not Client.
      参数:

    • readAllClients

      public static java.util.ArrayList<Client> readAllClients() throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
      Read DATA_PATH to the program and convert it to POJO using fastJSON.
      返回:
      all data in DATA_PATH
      抛出:
      java.io.FileNotFoundException - when DATA_PATH not found

    • writeAll

      private static void writeAll​(java.util.ArrayList<Client> clients) throws java.io.IOException
      Write all clients in ArrayList to the file using fastJSON. This method will overwrite the DATA_PATH file, so this method is set to be private to protect the data.
      参数:
      clients - the Client data that you want to write
      抛出:
      java.io.IOException - when IO issue occur
